  "body": "# ðŸš€ Feature Request\r\n\r\nLocal memory for 4k validators slowly grow:\r\n![Screen Shot 2020-05-22 at 10 39 08 AM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/21316537/82694670-869ff700-9c18-11ea-9073-72a7ff5efb74.png)\r\n\r\nFrom profiling heap, one weakness is the amount of head state copy in RPC to service attester and aggregator:\r\n<img width=\"1644\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-21 at 8 27 08 PM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/21316537/82694728-a33c2f00-9c18-11ea-9abf-194c7e4e3c21.png\">\r\n\r\nThis can be greatly improved by caching only one head state and use that across attester and aggregator",
